description: Located in the desirable Westwick neighborhood, this updated home seamlessly combines classic charm with modern features. The primary suite offers high ceilings and plenty of natural light. Enjoy community amenities like a pool, tennis courts, clubhouse, playground, and access to Addicks Dam bike trail. Conveniently situated near I-10 and Beltway 8, this property provides easy access for your commute and nearby dining/shopping in the Energy Corridor. The zoned SBISD elementary will change from Thornwood to Sherwood in August 2025.

description: Welcome to this modern and spacious home located Candlelight Place. This property has an open concept layout, perfect for entertaining and everyday living. The living area with a gas fireplace as its focal point, seamlessly connects both a dining space and cozy breakfast area. New luxury vinyl plank flooring flows throughout the main living areas and all bedrooms downstairs. The island kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring ample cabinet storage, generous countertop space and stainless steel appliances. The split floor plan ensures privacy, with the primary bedroom situated at the back of the home, complete with TWO walk-in closets. The primary bath offers double sinks, a vanity area, a jetted tub, and a separate shower. Additionally, downstairs you'll find a home office, two bedrooms and a full-size bath. Upstairs, a spacious game room awaits, along with a fourth bedroom and a full bath. Backyard has a covered patio and a nice side yard. EV charging is also available in the garage.

description: Super cute house on a quiet tree lined street with sidewalks in Kings Grant in Rockledge. Beautiful updated kitchen features warm wood cabinetry, granite countertops and stainless appliances plus a breakfast bar and breakfast nook! Large family room with sliders to the covered screened back porch and large backyard. Separate flex room is perfect for a home office, playroom, exercise room or second living room. Interior laundry room. No garage . . . no problem! Store all your stuff in your huge backyard shed! 2018 Roof, 2020 water heater, updated windows, exterior just painted. Convenient location near shops, restaurants, I-95 and even the beaches.

description: Welcome Home to this Beautiful Ranch Home In Union County on a Stunning Lot. Front Covered Porch leads into the Open Floor Plan Home. Chef’s Kitchen with Tiled Back-Splash, Recess Lights, Breakfast Bar, Large Pantry & Lots of Natural Light. Large Dining area and Huge Living Room with Vaulted Ceiling, Stunning Floors, Fireplace & French Doors Leading out to the Backyard Oasis. Beautiful Primary Suite w/Vaulted Ceiling, Large Closet & Primary Bathroom Suite. Split Bedroom Floor Plan with 2 More Large Bedrooms and Full Bathroom on the opposite side of the Home. Fenced Backyard Oasis with Screened in Back Patio, Huge Shed, and Trees line the Back of the Property for Privacy. Community Park, Playground, Multi-use field and Covered Pavilion.

description: Beautiful end unit Meridian townhome. Large fenced in patio area. The back gate opens to the walking/jogging path. Enjoy the nearby tennis courts. Just minutes from Folly Beach and Historic Charleston. The James Island County Park and Senior Center are about a mile away.  The  interior of the unit is very well maintained. Enjoy the spacious the family room and separate dining area.  Each bedroom has full bathroom.  Outdoor space is great for entertaining as well. The sellers have used this as a long term rental.  Short term rentals are not allowed.  The rentals must be 30 days or longer.

This lovely home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, a spacious detached laundry room, and a covered carport. Originally built in 1955, this home was renovated in 2022 and boats quality custom finishes throughout. The bright, spacious living room calls you in to the home, ready to host your movie nights or game nights and all of your holiday festivities. The fully fenced backyard will be your personal paradise. With it's patio and abundant greenery, you'll enjoy days and nights entertaining friends and family in the fresh air. This remarkable home is close to all Orlando has to offer including top notch shopping and dining, as well as Downtown Winter Par, Downtown Orlando, Amway Center, Dr. Phillips Performing Arts Center, Camping World Stadium, and more! You'll be able to attend Orlando's greatest events with a short commute. You don't want to miss out on this beautiful home in this neighborhood. Schedule your showing today!

description: Architectural designed home located in San Luis Obispo's "Banana Belt".  Cul De Sac location offers privacy of a retreat within the Redwoods.  Entering into the front entry, the home welcomes you into a full space focusing on open concept encompassing sitting area,  living room, dining room and kitchen.  Floor to ceiling windows case the views of San Luis Obispo area mountains allowing all day natural light.  Three separate sliding glass doors from main living area are perfect for sunset viewing and BBQ entertaining. Several custom designed stained glass inserts embellish the ceiling height windows along with vaulted ceilings that feature cutouts framing the area foothills.  Two larger bedrooms have enough room for in-suite sitting areas to enjoy the same views as main living areas. Out the back door you walk into the secluded backyard that includes a greenhouse and aviary.  Several niches of opportunity for outdoor entertaining and/or relaxing with a favorite book.  One side of double car garage has a conversion to workshop/office and 1/2 bath.  Please refer to the 3D walking tour throughout the home which represents the detail in design of this very special home.

description: Beautiful Move in Ready home nestled in the heart of Seven Hills! Brand new flooring and paint! This is the best location you can choose! Enjoy your backyard that overlooks Allegro Park without the hassle of maintaining a pool. Just walk a few steps down the street and you have a community pool and spa! This neighborhood is near all of the trendy stores, casinos and major freeways. Also, the home is within minutes of the Raiders Practice Facility.  The Primary Bedroom is probably the biggest you will ever see with a HUGE sitting room and is separate from the other bedrooms. Granite counters in the kitchen with an undermount sink and includes all of the appliances. There is a 2 way fireplace in between the Living Room and Family Room that will surely keep you toasty on our cool wintery nights. Walking in the door to this open floorplan will definitely make you feel like you're home!

description: Welcome to 6 Raven Drive. Situated on a premium lot,this beautiful brick front Colonial style home boasts 4 Bedrooms and 4 Bathrooms.   Located in the much sought after community of Heritage Woods Old Bridge with its excellent schools. Home features a 2 story entrance, 9' ceilings, kitchen with granite counters, tile backsplash and stainless steel appliances, hardwood floors throughout the 1st and 2nd floor,full finished basement with 1/2 bath, summer kitchen, rec room, bar, and utility room. Home is equipped with a Generac Whole House Generater, a 2 car garage, fenced in rear property, and a professionally landscaped property complete this fine home. Home was just professionally painted. if you're looking for a move-in ready condition home, look no further, this is it. Close to major road ways Rt 9, Rt 18, & GSP. Close to shopping and bus line to NYC. Hurry, this one wont last !

description: Welcome to carefree living in this meticulously maintained, move-in ready end unit ranch condo in desirable Society Hill! This beautiful home begins with an open floor plan that includes a spacious living room that flows seamlessly into the dining room and kitchen, complete with a pantry and center island. The primary suite features a full bathroom with a stall shower and a closet. Two additional bedrooms and another full bathroom provide even more living space to be enjoyed. Sliding doors in both the living room and primary bedroom lead to a sunroom, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the serene views of the lake under the glistening natural light. Enjoy outdoor living on the patio in your private backyard, surrounded by a wood privacy fence with direct access to the pond. Assigned parking ensures convenience, and you'll have access to fantastic community amenities including a clubhouse, pool, tennis courts, and more! With its prime location near Routes 9, 18, and 34 and local bus transportation, this condo offers everything you could need and more!

description: Welcome to this breathtaking east-facing townhouse in pristine condition, nestled in the highly sought-after Lexington Village community. This stunning end-unit home boasts crown molding, recessed lighting, and an abundance of windows that flood the space with natural light. Renovated in 2018, this property features a newer roof, windows, modern bathrooms, stylish tile and beautiful laminate flooring on the first floor, with cozy carpeting upstairs. You'll also find convenient garage storage shelves and much more. At the heart of the home is the updated chef's kitchen, complete with high-end stainless steel appliances, exquisite cabinetry, and luxurious granite countertops. The spacious living and dining room area, adorned with a charming wood-burning fireplace, is perfect for entertaining family and friends. A chic powder room adds a touch of sophistication to the main level. Upstairs, the primary bedroom offers two generous closets, a ceiling fan, and a tastefully appointed private bath. Two additional well-sized bedrooms, each featuring walk-in closets and ceiling fans, share a thoughtfully designed main bath, while a conveniently located laundry room completes this floor. Step outside to your professionally landscaped oasis, where you can enjoy unobstructed views of the surrounding open space and direct access to the community's scenic walking trail. The three-zone underground irrigation system ensures your yard remains lush and inviting. This home is ideally situated near Rt 18, Rt 1, the NJ Turnpike, downtown New Brunswick, Rutgers University, and major hospitals, with easy access to houses of worship, NYC buses, shopping, dining, and recreational activities. Plus, it falls within the award-winning East Brunswick Blue Ribbon Schools district! Don't miss your chance to make this magnificent townhouse your new home.

description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart the Littlebook neighborhood in Princeton. This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath contemporary home blends sleek, modern design with comfortable living, offering the perfect retreat for anyone seeking both style and convenience. Step inside and be greeted by a floor plan that boasts abundant of natural light, thanks to the many windows throughout the first floor. Enjoy cooking in the updated kitchen featuring top-tier stainless steel appliances, elegant granite countertops, and custom cabinetry, perfect for both everyday meals and special gatherings. The kitchen also offers an eating area with sliding doors out to the garden. The living room is spacious and airy with access to the outside through double sliding doors. It offers a marble fireplace and is ideal for entertaining guests or relaxing with family with. In addition to this there is also a powder room on the first floor. On the second floor you will find a generously sized bedroom with an updated bathroom attached. The laundry room is also located on this floor. The primary suite is a few steps up from the second floor and it features a beautiful sitting area with a fireplace, a large bathroom and plenty of closet space. The third bedroom is located on this floor as well. The home's outdoor space is just as impressive—this is truly a gardener’s dream, with a beautifully landscaped front and backyard. In the back you will enjoy the spacious patio, ideal for summer barbecues or simply enjoying the peaceful surroundings. Situated just minutes from downtown Princeton, you'll have access to world-class dining, shopping, and the renowned Princeton University. Plus, with excellent schools, parks, and easy access to major highways, this home offers the perfect balance of serenity and accessibility.

description: Welcome to 3 Fleetwood Drive, located in the heart of Hamilton Square. This three bedroom, one and a half bath is ready to be your next home! Enter into the open living room with all new flooring that spills into the large kitchen. Double glass doors lead you out to the newly poured concrete patio. The backyard is spacious and fenced for your outdoor enjoyment and entertaining. A separate entrance into the mudroom for convenient storage and access to the attached garage.  This home is lovingly maintained and enhanced. Upgrades include: new roof and siding (2022), renovated main bathroom, poured concrete patios, two year old fan coil and furnace. The basement also has two sump pumps with a backup system and an irrigation loop in the backyard.  Just a short walk to Sayen House and Botanical Gardens. And close to nearby restaurants, shops and parks. This location is ideal for commuting to New York with Hamilton Rail Station nearby; easy access to I-195, I-295, and the New Jersey Turnpike.
